narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: General knowledge and intuition at the molecular scale. Method in protein-protein interaction, network, kinetics, and etc.
I developed an intuition on the scale of things in biology

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Sometimes I felt the organization of the class is not as well planned. however, that degree of flexibility is actually what makes it more engaging than any typical class.
I think this course was very engaging and fun
I like that the class was very interactive/conversational. The homeworks were very helpful and also pretty fun to work on. A few more problems about interactions would have been helpful for me

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Very entertaining class in group. A lot of great in class activities to explore various aspect of molecular scale.
yes! this was one of my favorite classes
